###Gherkin Steps for Login Feature

Feature: Login feature
Scenario: As a valid user I can log into my app via Notifications screen
   When I see "Browse categories"
   And I press "Navigate up"
   And I press "Notifications"
   And I press "Log in"
   Then I enter text "My_email" into field with id "Email_id"
   Then I enter text "My_password" into field with id "Password_id"
   Then I press "Log in"
   Then I should see "Notifications"
   And I press "Navigate up"
   And I press "My account"
   Then I scroll down
   And I press "Log out"
   And I press "Confirm"

